version-checking code to get a

00:17:01.986 --> 00:17:02.986 A:middle
different image for the

00:17:02.986 --> 00:17:03.696 A:middle
different OSs.

00:17:04.366 --> 00:17:06.816 A:middle
Just provide 2 images with the

00:17:06.886 --> 00:17:08.496 A:middle
same name, and it works out of

