00:19:59.176 --> 00:20:00.796 A:middle
So images can change size

00:19:59.176 --> 00:20:00.796 A:middle
So images can change size

00:20:00.796 --> 00:20:01.756 A:middle
dynamically, and we have to talk

00:20:01.756 --> 00:20:02.896 A:middle
about this, because you usually

00:20:02.896 --> 00:20:04.706 A:middle
want to constrain an image by

00:20:04.706 --> 00:20:05.256 A:middle
width and height.

00:20:06.186 --> 00:20:08.826 A:middle
And since a symbol renders

00:20:09.126 --> 00:20:11.106 A:middle
always -- it's a vector.

00:20:12.136 --> 00:20:13.706 A:middle
You could be inclined to always

00:20:13.756 --> 00:20:14.816 A:middle
specify this width and height,

00:20:14.946 --> 00:20:16.046 A:middle
but it's actually not a good

00:20:16.046 --> 00:20:16.396 A:middle
idea.

00:20:17.056 --> 00:20:18.586 A:middle
First of all, it's not really

00:20:18.586 --> 00:20:18.876 A:middle
correct.

00:20:19.516 --> 00:20:21.126 A:middle
You can see on the screenshot

00:20:21.126 --> 00:20:23.046 A:middle
that the symbol is described as

00:20:23.046 --> 00:20:24.776 A:middle
a 17-point symbol, which is

00:20:24.776 --> 00:20:27.456 A:middle
really small, but it still

00:20:27.456 --> 00:20:28.996 A:middle
renders as a very large image,

00:20:29.666 --> 00:20:30.806 A:middle
because the width and height are

00:20:30.806 --> 00:20:31.046 A:middle
there.

00:20:31.806 --> 00:20:32.836 A:middle
But you can also see that it's

00:20:32.836 --> 00:20:34.496 A:middle
not entirely correctly centered.

00:20:34.496 --> 00:20:35.486 A:middle
Like, it's a little bit off to

00:20:35.486 --> 00:20:36.546 A:middle
the left, and a little bit off

00:20:36.546 --> 00:20:37.436 A:middle
to the top.

00:20:37.576 --> 00:20:40.856 A:middle
And secondly, it's not

00:20:40.856 --> 00:20:41.916 A:middle
performance -- this is not the

00:20:41.916 --> 00:20:43.776 A:middle
most performance way to display

00:20:43.776 --> 00:20:44.626 A:middle
a symbol image.

00:20:45.636 --> 00:20:49.676 A:middle
So what you want to do is not

00:20:49.706 --> 00:20:50.936 A:middle
constrain the symbol image at

00:20:50.936 --> 00:20:52.336 A:middle
all, and have it be its natural

00:20:52.336 --> 00:20:52.696 A:middle
size.

00:20:53.416 --> 00:20:57.526 A:middle
In this case, we changed the

00:20:57.526 --> 00:20:59.736 A:middle
size of the symbol to 500 points

00:20:59.796 --> 00:21:00.756 A:middle
to match the size that we had

00:20:59.796 --> 00:21:00.756 A:middle
to match the size that we had

