typographic information in the

00:23:48.436 --> 00:23:50.546 A:middle
symbol and use it to properly

00:23:50.546 --> 00:23:52.606 A:middle
visually align the symbol versus

00:23:52.806 --> 00:23:53.746 A:middle
the piece of text, and that

00:23:53.746 --> 00:23:55.706 A:middle
might actually happen that the

00:23:55.706 --> 00:23:59.136 A:middle
frames of the two elements are

00:23:59.136 --> 00:24:00.096 A:middle
not matching up together.

00:23:59.136 --> 00:24:00.096 A:middle
not matching up together.

